rows.label: tlk70000073_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Ha! Never thought the kind,
gentle- hearted Emperor Hugo
could be such a villain!

rows.label: tlk70000073_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Well, you did save my skin,
so I'm grateful for that.

rows.label: tlk70000073_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Danger goes hand in hand with being a
spy, but profit sadly does not. This
debacle's a fine example of that.

rows.label: tlk70000073_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Well, I saw it coming
sooner or later. I wasn't
exactly getting homesick.

rows.label: tlk70000073_02_msg0005
rows.name:
Right, time to start afresh!
...Soon as I get used to strutting
around in this new getup.
